      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. GULL WING comes off an average effort last start when sixth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Zipping Lowens (30.74) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Can make amends. 6. PSYCHO CIRCUS hit the frame latest (29.76) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and can measure up. 8. BOSTON STRONG has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when second (30.23) at this track in a Grade 5. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Rates a winning chance on best. 3. JIGSAW BILLY is last start winner who looks one of the chances.\",\"runners\":[2,6,8,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
